<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f6f8fb;">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Your Free Trial is Ending Soon | Project Athlete 360</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f6f8fb;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #1f2937;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #00b4d8);
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .header img {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 45px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .content h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
        color: #111827;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #374151;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .highlight {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #007bff;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 28px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .cta-button:hover {
        background: #005fcc;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 25px 40px;
        font-size: 13px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .expiry-box {
        background: #f0f9ff;
        border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <img src="https://pa360.net/logo.png" alt="Project Athlete 360" />
        <h2>Project Athlete 360</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Hello {{name}},</h1>

        <div class="expiry-box">
          ⏳ Your <span class="highlight">Free Trial</span> ends in 
          <strong>7 days ({{expiryDate}})</strong>.
        </div>

        <p>
          It’s been great having you on board! Over the past few weeks, you’ve
          seen how <strong>Project Athlete 360</strong> brings performance tracking,
          athlete management, and institutional analytics together in one smart platform.
        </p>

        <p>
          To keep your data, analytics, and connected athletes active, you’ll
          need to choose a plan before your trial ends.
        </p>

        <p>
          Upgrading ensures <strong>no data loss</strong> and continued access to your
          dashboard, insights, and AI tools.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
          <a href="{{upgradeLink}}" class="cta-button">Upgrade My Plan</a>
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 25px;">
          Don’t lose your momentum — keep growing stronger with science and community.
          <br /><br />
          — The <strong>Project Athlete 360</strong> Team
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          You’re receiving this email because you’re using a Project Athlete 360 trial account.
          Your trial will expire in 7 days.<br />
          Need help choosing the right plan? Contact 
          <a href="mailto:support@pa360.net">support@pa360.net</a>.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">
          &copy; {{year}} Project Athlete 360. All rights reserved.<br />
          <a href="https://pa360.net">pa360.net</a> • 
          <a href="https://projectathlete360.com">projectathlete360.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>